column5: Does anyone have any curent info the how the walleye and catfish bite is going ?
walleyes are listed as fair & catfishing is always good. Bigger cats north of Lockport.
"Oakhammock101" <[email protected]> Email this guy, had a great time on the Red back in june with him!
Already reports of the odd greenback being caught in the red. We are still getting great numbers of cats, 15 - 25 cats per 4 - 6 hour trip.
